      <title>日本保险公司债券账面损失翻倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/paper-losses-on-bonds-double-for-japan-s-insurers-as-rates-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于利率上升，日本四大寿险公司持有的国内债券账面损失较 3 月份结束的财年增长了一倍多，不过自 6 月份以来，这些公司已经收回了部分损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/paper-losses-on-bonds-double-for-japan-s-insurers-as-rates-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 07:07:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
